The Fisher information matrix diagonal entries:
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{alignat}{1}
I_{pp}(\theta) & =\mathbb{E}\left[\left(\sum_{k=1}^{N}\frac{1}{l_{k}}\frac{\partial l_{k}}{\partial c_{p}}\right)^{2}\right]\nonumber \\
